item.title: Area Births – Washington Times Herald
item.description: Friday, January 26, 2018 4:57 PM. Area Births. Washington Times Herald. Retrieved from http://www.washtimesherald.com/ Area Births Oliver Deno Jan. 15, 2018 Phyllis Hodges and Bryant Deno of Washington announce the birth of their son, Oliver James Loren-Lee Deno. He was born Jan. 15 at Daviess Community Hospital. He weighed 4 lbs., 11 ozs. and was 19 inches long. He is welcomed by William Henry, 19, Katie June, 17, Karah Elizabeth, 13, Emma Grace, 7, Wyatt James, 5, Elias Daniel Marc-Lee, 3, Emerson David Foster, 18 months.
